comments: Young (TOR) and Williams (BOS) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Theis (BOS) is already in Barnes' (TOR) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Barnes (TOR) moves forward into Smart's (BOS) path and initiates contact that affects his FOM off ball.
White (BOS) and Young (TOR) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Anunoby (TOR) is already in Nesmith's (BOS) path and is firming up when contact occurs.  The two then come together at the same spot after the initial contact as they move towards the basket.
Nesmith (BOS) moves slightly forward towards VanVleet (TOR) and marginal contact occurs at the end of the drive.
Young (TOR) and Theis (BOS) mutually engage and disengage during the rebound.
Siakam (TOR) and Smart (BOS) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Theis (BOS) is already in Trent Jr.'s (TOR) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Theis (BOS) brings his forearm towards Young (TOR) and marginal contact occurs as he releases from the contact.
Trent Jr. (TOR) is moving alongside Smart's (BOS) path and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Smart (BOS) brings his arm towards Trent Jr.'s (TOR) side and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Smart (BOS) is already in Trent Jr.'s (POR) path with his legs within the frame of his body, and Smart does not deliver the contact.
Theis (BOS) is moving alongside Siakam's (TOR) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Theis (BOS) is retreating his arms into a vertical position when marginal contact occurs with Siakam (TOR) during the driving shot attempt.
White (BOS) and Trent Jr. (TOR) briefly engage and disengage on the perimeter.
Theis (BOS) briefly grasps Young's (TOR) arm and marginal contact occurs as the defenders switch.
Theis (BOS) and Trent Jr. (TOR) briefly engage and disengage as Theis is rolling towards the rim.
Trent Jr. (TOR) briefly grasps Theis' (BOS) arm and marginal contact occurs off ball in the post.
Young (TOR) is moving alongside Smart's (BOS) path and Smart loses control of the ball on his own as he enters his upward shooting motion.
VanVleet (TOR) brings his hands towards Nesmith (BOS) and marginal contact occurs as VanVleet moves to set the pick.

Replay review of the foul called on Nesmith (BOS) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Nesmith steps forward into Siakam's (TOR) path and initiates contact as Siakam is starting his upward shooting motion.
Trent Jr. (TOR) goes to not through Theis' (BOS) space during the screen.
Anunoby (TOR) is moving alongside Williams' (BOS) path and Williams loses control of the ball on his own.
As the Raptors gain possession, Coach Nurse (TOR) attempts to call a timeout, which is not recognized by the crew.
Williams (BOS) is already in Trent Jr.'s (TOR) path and does not deliver contact as the defenders switch.
Trent Jr. (TOR) wraps Williams (BOS) off ball.
Young (TOR) and Smart (BOS) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.  The reaction from Smart is not consistent with the contact from Young.
VanVleet (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Williams (BOS) as he defends the shot near the rim.
VanVleet (TOR) loses control of the ball on his own prior to any contact from Nesmith (BOS).
Siakam (TOR) is moving alongside White's (BOS) path and cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt.
Nesmith (BOS) makes contact with Young's (TOR) arm that causes Young to lose control of the rebound.
Theis (BOS) briefly grasps Young's (TOR) arm and immediately releases his arm as they attempt to secure the rebound.
Smart (BOS) cleanly dislodges the ball from Young (TOR) during rebounding.
After initially making contact with the ball, Nesmith (BOS) slides his hand off of the ball and makes contact with Young's (TOR) arm as he is passing the ball.
Siakam (TOR) jumps forward and delivers contact to Williams (BOS) as they attempt to secure the rebound.
Young (TOR) is already in White's (BOS) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Williams (BOS) and Achiuwa (TOR) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Trent Jr. (TOR) swipes his hand down and makes contact with White's (BOS) arm as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Nesmith (BOS) commits a take foul on Trent Jr. (TOR).
Williams (BOS) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Young (TOR) legally contests Williams' (BOS) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
